---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Cards from "../../components/Cards.astro";
---

<Layout title="About – Raúl Abad" lang="en">
  <section
    class="sm:flex items-center justify-between gap-12 w-full mb-20 mt-8"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-xl">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-sky-300">
        Full‑Stack Developer · Symfony · Angular · Drupal
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white">
          Hi, I’m <span class="text-sky-300">Raúl Abad</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-100/90">
          Web developer with 4+ years of experience designing, building and
          maintaining web applications for digital products and international
          projects.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-200/90">
        I’m currently working as a <span class="font-semibold">Full‑Stack Developer at NeuronUP</span>,
        building and maintaining the product with Symfony and Angular, designing
        REST APIs and implementing new business‑driven features.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-200/80">
        Previously I worked at companies such as <span class="font-semibold">NTT DATA</span> and
        <span class="font-semibold"> Tefipro</span>, contributing to projects for the
        European public administration (ESMA, ERC, UNDRR, UN‑NEWS) and Industry
        4.0 solutions. I enjoy tackling complex challenges, understanding
        stakeholder needs and turning them into reliable, scalable software.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-2">
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-sky-200 border border-sky-500/40"
          >Symfony · Angular · Drupal</span
        >
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500/15 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-100 border border-emerald-500/40"
          >PHP · JavaScript · Node.js</span
        >
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/15 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-100 border border-indigo-500/40"
          >REST APIs · Docker · Git</span
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mt-0 flex justify-center">
      <img
        alt="Profile image"
        width="360"
        height="360"
        decoding="async"
        src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/raulabadt/portfolio/main/public/assets/perfil.jpg"
        class="rounded-full ring-4 ring-sky-400/60 shadow-2xl shadow-sky-900/40 object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="flex flex-col items-center w-full mb-16 mt-4">
    <h2
      class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl max-w-2xl text-center font-semibold text-white"
    >
      Beyond code, I like to stay active, keep learning and disconnect with
      hobbies that help me balance creativity and focus.
    </h2>
  </section>

  <Cards />
</Layout>


